ygData.messageBody:
Where did you get a rebreather? I heard that it cost 1000pp for components
for a gnome to attempt to make one.

Sylly

p.s. the one and only time I was in Kedge - I had EB cast on me but had
Aquatic Ayre memmed just in case (or more like when.) But having to rely on
Ayre - means one less song you can twist - although ayre seems to have an
extended linger time - like aria used to.
